      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies. This example is a true driver\u2019s car, boasting a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure long-term valvetrain reliability. The rod bearings have been proactively replaced, and the 6-speed manual transmission provides precise engagement through every gate. While the car exhibits minor cosmetic patina, the suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in and lateral stability. A compression test confirms the engine remains within factory tolerances, delivering linear power all the way to its 8,000 RPM redline.",
